description:
Hero Quest BG is a translation of the popular boardgame Hero Quest in Bulgarian made by myself.
At first I translated the game for my personal use but at some time I decide to share it with the community because I believe that it could be useful to other fans interested in the boardgaming and can bring fun not only to me. :)

The package contains all needed elements, ready to be printed and then played. In fact if you download and print the materials for this release of the game you will not need any other things from the original game. All the plastic miniatures and the furnitures are replaced by paper models that you can fold by yourself. These models can not be found on any other place on internet. They are all made especially for this release of the game by me (except for the furniture models that I took from worldworksgames - sorry guys I admire your work but I couldnÃƒÂ¢Ã¢â€šÂ¬Ã¢â€žÂ¢t found nothing else that I could use).
