All the materials were collected from various sites over the internet then prepeared for quality printing. They are all packed in PDF documents A4 format on 300 dpi !!!

The translation and preparation for printing of the materials took me somewhere a year I think and it was hell of a work, so give credits.

If you don't understand Bulgarian ... sorry about that.
I left the original books in english too, but the cards are all translated. Anyway you can still download this torrent and use the paper miniatures and the supplementary materials some of which are 2 pc games, some videos and other cool stuff that i collected for the last year.


